  "details": "Heap-based buffer overflow in the qtdemux_parse_samples function in gst/qtdemux/qtdemux.c in GStreamer Good Plug-ins (aka gst-plugins-good) 0.10.9 through 0.10.11 might allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary code via crafted Composition Time To Sample (ctts) atom data in a malformed QuickTime media .mov file.",
